description: Use this API to retrieve the status of the shipping document task.

parameters.name: shipping_id
parameters.description: Shopeepay transaction identifier for a shipping

parameters.name: shipping_document_task
parameters.description: The task of shipping document manifest

response_fields.name: request_id
response_fields.description: The identifier for an API request (for error tracking)

response_fields.name: warning
response_fields.description: Simple warning message (no actual task error)

response_fields.name: result_id
response_fields.description: The ID of the result task

response_fields.name: status
response_fields.description: The status of the shipping document task (no shipping task exists)

response_fields.name: file_error
response_fields.description: Indicate error type if any occurred for error

response_fields.name: file_message
response_fields.description: Indicate error details if any occurred to error
